PhpRestService
==============

* Introduction
* Features
* Requirements


Introduction
------------
PhpRestService is a library for creating RESTful webservices with PHP. 


Features
--------
* Create RESTful Resources within minutes
* Multiple input formats (http arguments, json, xml, etc)
* Multiple output formats (xml, json, etc)
* Handles content negotiation
* Supports compression & caching
* Uses http response codes properly


Requirements
------------
* PHP 5.3
* Webserver (apache, nginx)

